div.p:
Well, you believe in GOD, believe also in CHRIST the light that hath visited you: And if you truly believe, you will not make haste: You will not make haste out of the hour of judgment;


you will stay the time of your trial and cleansing, that you may be as I said,
as pure as gold seven times tried;
and so receive the LORD's mark and stamp, his image and approbation; that you may be his throughout, in body, soul and spirit; sealed to him in an eternal covenant.
